<p class="p22 f106">Keynote 1: <br><span class="f107"><a href="#anchor5">Process Signature  Knowledge-based approach towards function-oriented manufacturing - Bernhard Karpuschewski</a></span></p>
<p class="p22 f106">Keynote 2: <br><span class="f107"><a href="#anchor4">Surface integrity in civil nuclear industry - Philippe Gilles</a></span></p>
<p class="p22 f106">Keynote 3: <br><span class="f107"><a href="#anchor2">From Process Signature to Digital Twin for Part Surface Integrity in Manufacturing - Thomas Bergs</a></span></p>
<p class="p22 f106">Keynote 4: <br><span class="f107"><a href="#anchor1">Surface Integrity in Machining Aerospace Materials and Its Impact on Functional Performance</a></span><span class="f107"><a href="#anchor1"> - M. Helmi Attia</a></span></p>
<p class="p22 f106">Keynote 5: <br><span class="f107"><a href="#anchor3">On the use of nanomechanical testing to characterize transformations of materials induced by surface manufacturing processes - Guillaume Kermouche</a></span></p>
